nt institutions, and buyers through a unified system that drives productivity, sustainability, and inclusive economic growth.\nAt the core of IFU is a transformative model that integrates technology, data, and global trade to expand market access, strengthen rural economies, and improve livelihoods for farming communities worldwide.\n<BR><BR>\nWhat sets IFU apart is its integrated impact system\u2014where agricultural trade is directly linked to social development. Through the IFU Impact Fund, revenues generated across the platform are reinvested into farmer training, rural development, and school meal programs, helping to reduce hunger and build long-term resilience in rural communities across the world.\n<BR><BR>\nOperating from the Washington DC metro area, United States of America, IFU is structured to function as both a global cooperative enterprise and a mission-driven development platform, supported by strong governance, expert leadership, and a network of international partners.\nTogether, IFU is building a future where agriculture becomes a driver of opportunity, equity, and global food security. \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/p>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div><!-- \/.about-one__text-box -->\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"about-one__inner\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"about-one__inner__content\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div><!-- \/.about-one__inner__content -->\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div><!-- \/.about-one__inner -->\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"about-one__button wow fadeInUp\" data-wow-duration=\"1500ms\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"#\"   class=\"cherito-btn\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"cherito-btn__text\">Discover More<\/span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"cherito-btn__hover cherito-btn__hover--1\"><\/span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"cherito-btn__hover cherito-btn__hover--2\"><\/span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"cherito-btn__hover cherito-btn__hover--3\"><\/span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"cherito-btn__ho