ge{\n  background-image:url();\n}\n#uc_content_carousel_new_elementor_6b1f9a8_item6 .carousel-image{\n  background-image:url();\n}\n#uc_content_carousel_new_elementor_6b1f9a8_item7 .carousel-image{\n  background-image:url();\n}\n#uc_content_carousel_new_elementor_6b1f9a8_item8 .carousel-image{\n  background-image:url();\n}\n#uc_content_carousel_new_elementor_6b1f9a8_item9 .carousel-image{\n  background-image:url();\n}\n\n\n<\/style>\n\n<div class=\"ue-content-carousel\" >\n  <div class=\"uc_carousel owl-carousel owl-theme uc-items-wrapper  uc-remote-parent  \" id=\"uc_content_carousel_new_elementor_6b1f9a8\" data-lightbox=\"false\" data-equal-height=\"false\"  data-remoteid='auto' data-widgetname='Content Carousel' data-sync='true' data-syncid='group1' >\n    <div id=\"uc_content_carousel_new_elementor_6b1f9a8_item1\" class=\"uc_image_carousel_container_holder ue-item\">\n  \n  \n      <div class=\"uc_image_carousel_content content-padding ue-content-holder\">\n\n              <div class=\"uc_image_carousel_content-wrapper\">\n                                    <div class=\"ue-title\">AgriNexus<\/div>\n                      \n          <div class=\"ue-text\"><p>AgriNexus brings farmers, businesses, experts and organizations together in one trusted global network to collaborate, share knowledge and grow together.<\/p><hr \/><p>\u00a0<\/p><p>\ud83d\udc65 Expand Your Network: Connect with verified farmers, buyers, suppliers and experts worldwide.<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><p><strong class=\"Yjhzub\" data-sfc-root=\"c\" data-sfc-cb=\"\" data-processed=\"true\">\ud83c\udfaf<\/strong>\u00a0Access Opportunities: Find partnerships, projects and opportunities that grow your agriculture.<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><p>\ud83d\udca1 Share &amp; Learn: Exchange knowledge, experiences and best practices across the world.<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><p>\ud83d\udcca Grow Together: Build strong relationships that create long-term impact.<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><p><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\">Who Benefits:<\/span><\/p><p>Farmers | Agri-businesses | Cooperatives | Investors | Organizations<\/p><\/div>          <div class=\"ue-text\"><\/div>        <\/div>\n        \n                      <div class=\"ue-btn-holder\" style=\"width:100%;\">\n                              <a class=\"ue-btn uc_more_btn uc_button none elementor-animation-grow\"  href=\"https:\/\/internationalfarmunion.com\/platforms\/agrinexus\/\" >\n                  \n                  <div class=\"ue-btn-inner-wrapper\">\n                     \n                      <div class=\"ue-btn-inner-txt\"><span>Explore AgriNexus<\/span><\/div>\n                    \n                    \n                  <\/div>                <\/a>            <\/div>\n          \n        \n      \n      \n    <\/div>  <\/div>\n<div id=\"uc_content_carousel_new_elementor_6b1f9a8_item2\" class=\"uc_image_carousel_container_holder ue-item\">\n  \n  \n      <div class=\"uc_image_carousel_content content-padding ue-content-holder\">\n\n              <div class=\"uc_image_carousel_content-wrapper\">\n                                    <div class=\"ue-title\">AgriAcademie<\/div>\n                      \n          <div class=\"ue-text\"><p>AgriAcademie is the global learning and training engine of the IFU ecosystem. It provides access to agricultural education, practical training, expert knowledge, and global courses\u2014all in one place.<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><p>More than a learning platform, AgriAcademie is where knowledge becomes\u00a0skills, confidence, and real-world impact.<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><p>AgriAcademie operates as a\u00a0smart, flexible, and inclusive learning platform, integrated within the IFU ecosystem:<\/p><ul><li>\ud83c\udf93\u00a0Global Courses\u00a0\u2013 Access IFU and partner training programs<\/li><li>\ud83c\udf31\u00a0Practical Learning\u00a0\u2013 Real-world farming, business, and technology skills<\/li><li>\ud83c\udf0d\u00a0Localized Content\u00a0\u2013 Training adapted by country and region<\/li><li>\ud83e\udd16\u00a0AI Learning Support\u00a0\u2013 Personalized guidance and recommendations<\/li><li>\ud83d\udee1\ufe0f\u00a0Trusted Providers\u00a0\u2013 Courses reviewed and scored through AgriShield<\/li><li>\ud83d\udd17\u00a0Ecosystem Integration\u00a0\u2013 Connect learning to jobs, markets, and funding<\/li><\/ul><p>\u00a0<\/p><p>AgriAcademie doesn\u2019t just teach\u2014it prepares you to\u00a0apply knowledge in real life.<\/p><\/div>          <div class=\"ue-text\"><\/div>        <\/div>\n        \n                      <div class=\"ue-btn-holder\" style=\"width:100%;\">\n                              <a class=\"ue-btn uc_more_btn uc_button none elementor-animation-grow\"  href=\"https:\/\/internationalfarmunion.com\/platforms\/agriacademie\/\" >\n                  \n                  <div class=\"ue-btn-inner-wrapper\">\n                     \n                      <div class=\"ue-btn-inner-txt\"><span>Explore AgriAcademie<\/span><\/div>\n                    \n                    \n                  <\/div>                <\/a>            <\/div>\n          \n        \n      \n      \n    <\/div>  <\/div>\n<div id=\"uc_content_carousel_new_elementor_6b1f9a8_item3\" class=\"uc_image_carousel_container_holder ue-item\">\n  \n  \n      <div class=\"uc_image_carousel_content content-padding ue-content-holder\">\n\n              <div class=\"uc_image_carousel_content-wrapper\">\n                                    <div class=\"ue-title\">AgriExchange<\/div>\n                      \n          <div class=\"ue-text\"><p>AgriExchange is the global trading and marketplace engine of the IFU ecosystem\u2014now extended to include IFU Agritourism experiences.<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><p>It enables farmers, cooperatives, businesses, and buyers to buy and sell agricultural products, while also allowing farms and rural communities to offer\u00a0agritourism experiences\u00a0to local and international visitors.<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><p>More than a marketplace, AgriExchange is where products and places become\u00a0opportunities, transactions, income, and cultural exchange.<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><p><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\">Agricultural Marketplace<\/span><\/p><ul><li>Global product listings (crops, livestock, inputs)<\/li><li>Direct buyer\u2013seller transactions<\/li><li>Secure payments and escrow systems<\/li><li>Logistics and delivery coordination<\/li><li>Real-time pricing and demand insights<\/li><\/ul><\/div>          <div class=\"ue-text\"><\/div>        <\/div>\n        \n                      <div class=\"ue-btn-holder\" style=\"width:100%;\">\n                              <a class=\"ue-btn uc_more_btn uc_button none elementor-animation-grow\"  href=\"https:\/\/internationalfarmunion.com\/platforms\/agriexchange\/\" >\n                  \n                  <div class=\"ue-btn-inner-wrapper\">\n                     \n                      <div class=\"ue-btn-inner-txt\"><span>Explore AgriExchange<\/span><\/div>\n                    \n                    \n                  <\/div>                <\/a>            <\/div>\n          \n        \n      \n      \n    <\/div>  <\/div>\n<div id=\"uc_content_carousel_new_elementor_6b1f9a8_item4\" class=\"uc_image_carousel_container_holder ue-item\">\n  \n  \n      <div class=\"uc_image_carousel_content content-padding ue-content-holder\">\n\n              <div class=\"uc_image_carousel_content-wrapper\">\n                                    <div class=\"ue-title\">AgriCapital<\/div>\n                      \n          <div class=\"ue-text\"><p>AgriCapital is the global finance and investment engine of the IFU ecosystem. It connects farmers, agribusinesses, cooperatives, investors, donors, and financial institutions\u2014enabling access to funding, investment opportunities, and financial tools across the agricultural value chain.<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><p>More than a funding platform, AgriCapital is where ideas, farms, and projects become\u00a0investable, scalable, and sustainable ventures.<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><p><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\">The Bigger Picture<\/span><\/p><p>AgriCapital is not just about funding. It\u2019s about\u00a0unlocking the financial power of agriculture.<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><p>By connecting capital with opportunity, AgriCapital helps build stronger farms, scalable businesses, and resilient food systems worldwide.<\/p><\/div>          <div class=\"ue-text\"><\/div>        <\/div>\n        \n                      <div class=\"ue-btn-holder\" style=\"width:100%;\">\n                              <a class=\"ue-btn uc_more_btn uc_button none elementor-animation-grow\"  href=\"https:\/\/internationalfarmunion.com\/platforms\/agricapital\/\" >\n                  \n                  <div class=\"ue-btn-inner-wrapper\">\n                     \n                      <div class=\"ue-btn-inner-txt\"><span>Explore AgriCapital<\/span><\/div>\n                    \n                    \n                  <\/div>                <\/a>            <\/div>\n          \n        \n      \n      \n    <\/div>  <\/div>\n<div id=\"uc_content_carousel_new_elementor_6b1f9a8_item5\" class=\"uc_image_carousel_container_holder ue-item\">\n  \n  \n      <div class=\"uc_image_carousel_content content-padding ue-content-holder\">\n\n              <div class=\"uc_image_carousel_content-wrapper\">\n                                    <div class=\"ue-title\">AgriFunds<\/div>\n                      \n          <div class=\"ue-text\"><p>AgriFunds is the global impact, nonprofit, and development engine of the IFU ecosystem.<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><p>It mobilizes resources, partnerships, and programs to support farmers, communities, and agricultural systems through training, food security initiatives, rural development, and sustainable agriculture projects.<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><p>More than a funding channel, AgriFunds is where support becomes\u00a0impact, resilience, and long-term transformation.<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><p><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\">Impact<\/span><\/p><p>AgriFunds is designed to shape the future of agricultural development:<\/p><ul><li>Transparent, data-driven impact systems<\/li><li>Global collaboration across sectors and regions<\/li><li>Scalable programs for long-term change<\/li><li>Integration of funding with education, markets, and innovation<\/li><\/ul><p>\u00a0<\/p><p>It transforms support into\u00a0measurable, lasting impact.<\/p><\/div>          <div class=\"ue-text\"><\/div>        <\/div>\n        \n                      <div class=\"ue-btn-holder\" style=\"width:100%;\">\n                              <a class=\"ue-btn uc_more_btn uc_button none elementor-animation-grow\"  href=\"https:\/\/internationalfarmunion.com\/platforms\/agrifunds\/\" >\n                  \n                  <div class=\"ue-btn-inner-wrapper\">\n                     \n                      <div class=\"ue-btn-inner-txt\"><span>Explore AgriFunds<\/span><\/div>\n                    \n                    \n                  <\/div>                <\/a>            <\/div>\n          \n        \n      \n      \n    <\/div>  <\/div>\n<div id=\"uc_content_carousel_new_elementor_6b1f9a8_item6\" class=\"uc_image_carousel_container_holder ue-item\">\n  \n  \n      <div class=\"uc_image_carousel_content content-padding ue-content-holder\">\n\n              <div class=\"uc_image_carousel_content-wrapper\">\n                                    <div class=\"ue-title\">AgriShield<\/div>\n                      \n          <div class=\"ue-text\"><p>AgriShield is the trust, compliance, and security engine of the IFU ecosystem. It protects users, verifies identities, monitors activities, and ensures that every interaction across the platform is transparent, secure, and reliable.<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><p>More than a security system, AgriShield is where trust becomes\u00a0measurable, enforceable, and visible.<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><p><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\">How<\/span> <span style=\"font-size: 20px;\">AgriShield Functions<\/span><\/p><p>AgriShield operates as a\u00a0real-time compliance and security layer, integrated across all IFU modules:<\/p><ul><li>\ud83c\udd94\u00a0Identity Verification (KYC\/KYB)\u00a0\u2013 Validate users and organizations<\/li><li>\ud83d\udcca\u00a0Trust Scoring System\u00a0\u2013 Assign credibility scores based on behavior and data<\/li><li>\ud83d\udd0d\u00a0Continuous Monitoring\u00a0\u2013 Detect suspicious activity and risks<\/li><li>\ud83d\udcc1\u00a0Compliance Management\u00a0\u2013 Ensure adherence to policies, regulations, and standards<\/li><li>\ud83d\udea8\u00a0Alert &amp; Enforcement System\u00a0\u2013 Notify and respond to threats or violations<\/li><li>\ud83d\udd17\u00a0Ecosystem Integration\u00a0\u2013 Protect interactions in AgriNexus, AgriExchange, AgriCapital, and beyond<\/li><\/ul><p>\u00a0<\/p><p>AgriShield transforms trust into a\u00a0structured, intelligent, and automated system.<\/p><\/div>          <div class=\"ue-text\"><\/div>        <\/div>\n        \n                      <div class=\"ue-btn-holder\" style=\"width:100%;\">\n                              <a class=\"ue-btn uc_more_btn uc_button none elementor-animation-grow\"  href=\"https:\/\/internationalfarmunion.com\/platforms\/agrishield\/\" >\n                  \n                  <div class=\"ue-btn-inner-wrapper\">\n                     \n                      <div class=\"ue-btn-inner-txt\"><span>Explore AgriShield<\/span><\/div>\n                    \n                    \n                  <\/div>                <\/a>            <\/div>\n          \n        \n      \n      \n    <\/div>  <\/div>\n<div id=\"uc_content_carousel_new_elementor_6b1f9a8_item7\" class=\"uc_image_carousel_container_holder ue-item\">\n  \n  \n      <div class=\"uc_image_carousel_content content-padding ue-content-holder\">\n\n              <div class=\"uc_image_carousel_content-wrapper\">\n                                    <div class=\"ue-title\">AgriCentral<\/div>\n                      \n          <div class=\"ue-text\"><p>AgriCentral is the operations and management engine of the IFU ecosystem. It provides a centralized environment where individuals, farms, cooperatives, businesses, and institutions can manage their activities, workflows, data, and teams\u2014all in one place. More than a management tool, AgriCentral is where operations become\u00a0organized, efficient, and scalable.How<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><p><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\">AgriCentral Works<\/span><\/p><p>AgriCentral operates as a\u00a0smart, centralized management platform, fully integrated within the IFU ecosystem:<\/p><ul><li>\ud83d\udcca\u00a0Dashboard &amp; Analytics\u00a0\u2013 Real-time overview of operations and performance<\/li><li>\ud83d\uddc2\ufe0f\u00a0Workflow Management\u00a0\u2013 Organize tasks, processes, and activities<\/li><li>\ud83d\udc65\u00a0Team &amp; Role Management\u00a0\u2013 Assign roles and manage access (RBAC)<\/li><li>\ud83d\udcb0\u00a0Financial Tracking\u00a0\u2013 Monitor revenue, expenses, and budgets<\/li><li>\ud83d\udcc1\u00a0Data Management\u00a0\u2013 Store and manage operational data securely<\/li><li>\ud83d\udee1\ufe0f\u00a0Compliance Integration\u00a0\u2013 Powered by AgriShield for governance and control<\/li><li>\ud83d\udd17\u00a0Ecosystem Integration\u00a0\u2013 Connect operations to markets, funding, training, and networking<\/li><\/ul><p>\u00a0<\/p><p>AgriCentral transforms daily operations into a\u00a0structured, transparent, and efficient system.<\/p><\/div>          <div class=\"ue-text\"><\/div>        <\/div>\n        \n                      <div class=\"ue-btn-holder\" style=\"width:100%;\">\n                              <a class=\"ue-btn uc_more_btn uc_button none elementor-animation-grow\"  href=\"https:\/\/internationalfarmunion.com\/platforms\/agricentral\/\" >\n                  \n                  <div class=\"ue-btn-inner-wrapper\">\n                     \n                      <div class=\"ue-btn-inner-txt\"><span>Explore AgriCentral<\/span><\/div>\n                    \n                    \n                  <\/div>                <\/a>            <\/div>\n          \n        \n      \n      \n    <\/div>  <\/div>\n<div id=\"uc_content_carousel_new_elementor_6b1f9a8_item8\" class=\"uc_image_carousel_container_holder ue-item\">\n  \n  \n      <div class=\"uc_image_carousel_content content-padding ue-content-holder\">\n\n              <div class=\"uc_image_carousel_content-wrapper\">\n                                    <div class=\"ue-title\">Data Engine<\/div>\n                      \n          <div class=\"ue-text\"><p>The IFU Data Engine is the intelligence and analytics engine of the entire IFU ecosystem. It collects, processes, and analyzes agricultural data from around the world\u2014transforming raw information into clear insights, predictions, and actionable decisions. More than a data system, the Data Engine is where information becomes\u00a0intelligence, foresight, and strategic advantage.<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><p><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\">How The Data Engine Works<\/span><\/p><p>The Data Engine operates as a\u00a0real-time data processing and analytics system, fully integrated across all IFU modules:<\/p><ul><li>\ud83d\udce1\u00a0Data Aggregation\u00a0\u2013 Collect data from global sources (markets, weather, production, trade)<\/li><li>\ud83d\udcca\u00a0Analytics &amp; Insights\u00a0\u2013 Transform data into meaningful information<\/li><li>\ud83e\udd16\u00a0AI &amp; Predictive Models\u00a0\u2013 Forecast trends, risks, and opportunities<\/li><li>\ud83c\udf0d\u00a0Country-Level Intelligence\u00a0\u2013 Provide localized insights by region<\/li><li>\ud83d\udcc8\u00a0Decision Support Tools\u00a0\u2013 Help users make informed choices<\/li><li>\ud83d\udd17\u00a0Ecosystem Integration\u00a0\u2013 Power AgriSphere, AgriNexus, AgriExchange, AgriCapital, and more<\/li><\/ul><p>\u00a0<\/p><p>The Data Engine turns complex data into a\u00a0clear, intelligent, and usable system.<\/p><\/div>          <div class=\"ue-text\"><\/div>        <\/div>\n        \n                      <div class=\"ue-btn-holder\" style=\"width:100%;\">\n                              <a class=\"ue-btn uc_more_btn uc_button none elementor-animation-grow\"  href=\"https:\/\/internationalfarmunion.com\/data-engine\/\" >\n                  \n                  <div class=\"ue-btn-inner-wrapper\">\n                     \n                      <div class=\"ue-btn-inner-txt\"><span>Explore Data Engine<\/span><\/div>\n                    \n                    \n                  <\/div>                <\/a>            <\/div>\n          \n        \n      \n      \n    <\/div>  <\/div>\n<div id=\"uc_content_carousel_new_elementor_6b1f9a8_item9\" class=\"uc_image_carousel_container_holder ue-item\">\n  \n  \n      <div class=\"uc_image_carousel_content content-padding ue-content-holder\">\n\n              <div class=\"uc_image_carousel_content-wrapper\">\n                                    <div class=\"ue-title\">AgriSphere<\/div>\n                      \n          <div class=\"ue-text\"><p>AgriSphere is a unified digital ecosystem designed to connect the entire agricultural world in one place.<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><p>It brings together farmers, buyers, investors, researchers, and institutions into a single intelligent platform\u2014where knowledge, markets, funding, and technology work together.<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><p>Instead of navigating disconnected tools and fragmented systems, AgriSphere gives you\u00a0one entry point into global agriculture.<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><p><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\">A Platform For Today and The Future<\/span><\/p><p>AgriSphere is designed not just for today\u2019s needs, but for the future of agriculture.<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><p><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\">Who Benefits:<\/span><\/p><p>Farmers | Learners &amp; Professionals | Buyers &amp; Businesses | Investors &amp; Institutions<\/p><\/div>          <div class=\"ue-text\"><\/div>        <\/div>\n        \n                      <div class=\"ue-btn-holder