ricultural journey remains the same\u2014preparing the land, growing food, supporting livelihoods, feeding communities, and creating opportunities for the future.<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><p>IFU\u2019s vision of \u201cOne World. One Agricultural Cycle.\u201d reflects the belief that global agriculture is strongest when farmers, institutions, technology, markets, and communities work together through one connected ecosystem designed to support resilience, innovation, and shared progress worldwide.<\/p><div>\u00a0<\/div><div>One Platform.<\/div><div>One Agricultural Cycle.<\/div><div>One Shared Global Mission.<\/div><\/div><p style=\"text-align: left;\">\u00a0<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-84385eb e-con-full e-flex e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"84385eb\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-71090eb elementor-widget elementor-widget-shortcode\" data-id=\"71090eb\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"shortcode.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-shortcode\">\n    <style>\n    .ifu-wrapper {\n        font-family: Inter, sans-serif;\n        background: #f5f5f5;\n        padding: 40px 20px;\n        overflow-x: hidden;\n    }\n\n    .ifu-glass {\n        background: rgba(255,255,255,0.75);\n        backdrop-filter: blur(10px);\n        border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.3);\n    }\n\n    .ifu-cycle-container {\n        position: relative;\n        width: 620px;\n        height: 620px;\n        margin: auto;\n        max-width: 100%;\n    }\n\n    .ifu-country-card {\n        min-width: 180px;\n        transition: all 0.3s ease;\n        cursor: pointer;\n    }\n\n    .ifu-country-card:hover {\n        transform: translateY(-5px);\n    }\n\n    .ifu-active-country {\n        border: 3px solid #2e7d32;\n        background: #f0fff4;\n    }\n\n    .ifu-no-scrollbar::-webk